<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="A" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Actaeon" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Actaeon,</orth> the Theban prince transformed to a stag by Diana: <bibl n="shak. tit 2.3.63" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. II, 3, 63</bibl>. His horns a prototype of cuckoldom: <bibl n="shak. wiv 2.1.122" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. II, 1, 122</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 3.2.44" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 44</bibl>.
